overview:
Mrs. Crabtree’s Creations focuses on our specialty of customized cakes and cupcakes based on a particular theme or occasion.

Our desserts are truly unique and we guarantee that you won’t find them at your local bakery. Our cakes not only look extraordinary, but taste delicious because they are always made fresh and homemade with alot of love and care. We have a variety of cake choices, fillings and frostings to choose from and we will customize your dessert any way we can to satisfy your sweet tooth. In addition to designing unique cakes, we also have a variety of delicious baked goods including cookies, chocolate covered pretzels and more. Mrs. Crabtree’s Creations is all about making dessert fun and the best part of any meal, that’s why her slogan is “Have Your Fun and Eat it, Too!” Serving Staten Island, Brooklyn, Queens, Manhattan, Bronx and parts of New Jersey and Long Island.
